                                    <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-7a44f84 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="7a44f84" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
                                        <div class="elementor-widget-container">
                                            <p>The Senior Executive Course lasts for 10 months, from February to November, each year and covers broadly such areas as:</p><ul><li>Foundation and Cultural Studies.</li><li>Research methodology.&nbsp;</li><li>Policy and Strategic Studies.</li><li>The Domestic Environment.&nbsp;</li><li>Regional Studies (Local and International).&nbsp;</li><li>Defense and Security (Domestic, Regional, and International).&nbsp;</li><li>International Relations and International organizations.&nbsp;</li><li>Science and Technology</li><li>Peace and Conflict/ Crisis Management</li></ul><p>In addition to these studies, Participants receive intensive training in Computer application and the French Language throughout the year.<br>The Course is run on a system of self-study. However, experienced and expert Guest Lecturers drawn from all sectors of life in the society, are tapped to stimulate the thinking of Participants.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>
                    <section class="elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-5c2bc56 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default" data-id="5c2bc56" data-element_type="section">
