                                                    <h2 class="ekit-heading--title elementskit-section-title  ekit-heading__title-has-border start">
                                                        Certificate of Attendance (COA)
                                                    </h2>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-d41203d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="d41203d" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
                                        <div class="elementor-widget-container">
                                            <p>A participant who fails to fulfill the minimum requirements for the award of membership of the National Institute (mni) may be recommended for the award of a certificate of attendance (COA).</p>
