                                                    </h2>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-418f609 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="418f609" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
                                        <div class="elementor-widget-container">
                                            <p>On the day prior to the Graduation Ceremony of the participants, which signifies the end of the Course, a distinguished personality is invited to deliver a lecture on a topic of his choice but which should be relevant to the institute’s mandate of moving the nation towards a better society. The fact that this event crowns the Studies programme for the course makes it one of the most important events, which precede the Graduation Ceremony.</p>
